your indigenous students
and your non-Indigenous students,

00:03:45.625 --> 00:03:50.029
and the indigenous students
that I work with, I share a language.

00:03:50.029 --> 00:03:53.266
I share different, ceremonies with them.

00:03:53.266 --> 00:03:55.101
I share like some are,

00:03:55.101 --> 00:03:57.804
some are more sacred
that that are to be shared

00:03:57.804 --> 00:03:59.272
like within the indigenous community,

00:03:59.272 --> 00:04:01.975
not necessarily
with the non-Indigenous community.

00:04:01.975 --> 00:04:04.344
So there's what I'm with.

00:04:04.344 --> 00:04:06.546
My little groups of students
are one on one.

00:04:06.546 --> 00:04:11.184
It can either be for like those kind
of teachings, like the deeper teachings.

00:04:11.551 --> 00:04:15.822
