to know their identity. And

00:05:23.189 --> 00:05:24.957
know it and share it,

00:05:24.957 --> 00:05:27.527
you know, and, I think

00:05:27.527 --> 00:05:30.296
as a, as a cultural support worker,

00:05:30.296 --> 00:05:33.299
I can be I can be a helpful stepping stone
in that process.

00:05:33.700 --> 00:05:37.003
And helping the kids to connect

00:05:37.003 --> 00:05:40.173
